                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:BlockQuote ;
                            oc:blockType "blockquote" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                            oc:quoteContent "\"This file was validated using LibreOffice. Please review in Microsoft PowerPoint before distribution, as rendering differences may exist.\"" ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "**LibreOffice is used for validation but DOES NOT render PowerPoint files accurately.** It will mangle fonts, gradients, shape positions, text wrapping, and some table formatting." ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                            oc:textContent "**Required action:** Always include this statement when delivering output:" ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                            oc:textContent "**What this means:** A slide that passes visual validation in LibreOffice may still have issues in Microsoft PowerPoint. The validation loop catches structural issues (missing content, broken tables, placeholder formatting retained) but **cannot** catch font substitution, subtle alignment shifts, or gradient problems." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 3 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "⚠️ Critical Rendering Limitation" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Table ;
                            oc:blockType "table" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                            oc:rowCount 6 ;
                            oc:tableCaption "These requirements are non-negotiable regardless of template" ;
                            oc:tableMarkdown """| Requirement | Details |
|-------------|---------|
| **Text Readability** | All text MUST have sufficient contrast with background. Examples: white/light text on dark blue, dark green, black backgrounds; black/dark text on white, light gray, light yellow backgrounds. |
| **Actual Table Objects** | Tabular data MUST be table objects, not tab-separated text. See [`xml-reference.md`](reference/xml-reference.md#table-implementation). |
| **Proper Chart/Table Sizing** | Pasted visuals MUST fill designated area. See [`formatting-standards.md`](reference/formatting-standards.md#chart-and-image-handling). |
| **Consistent Formatting** | Bullets within section MUST match (symbol, size, indent). Same-level boxes MUST use same font size. |
| **Content Boundaries** | All content MUST stay within slide edges. Footnote box width: ~32.5cm for 16:9, ~24cm for 4:3. |
| **No Placeholder Formatting** | Remove colored instruction boxes. Main body: dark text on light background per template. |
""" ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
